OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some sunny intervals.
OL,7,FSome clear spells at first tonight but
OL,8,Ftending to cloud over, perhaps a light
OL,9,Fshower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,12,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,13,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,14,Fwith some warm sunnier spells. Rather
OL,15,Fhumid.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,18,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,19,Fspells, though more cloud over Argyll
OL,20,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday. Perhaps some
OL,21,Fthundery showers later on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
